{"tid":45573,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"不讓位罪名","createTime":"2016-12-19T05:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T07:56:07.000Z","uid":8129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1ec315e7acb20e82f51ec5d043bf31f58c4f0bd","tid":45573,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"攰了嗎 坐低安竭有罪嗎<br />\n從坐位得到屋宇嗎<br />\n坐空位需要被批鬥嗎<br />\n<br />\n是我麼 仿似戲劇那樣假<br />\n如揭穿心裡的戲碼<br />\n露兇光關注避得到嗎<br />\n你說我刻意掩蓋 故看手機碌兩三次<br />\n我沒說出請坐美麉台詞<br />\n是我心中一種缺陷定義 溜進了眼角裡的刺<br />\n<br />\n為何不讓位亦是罪名 為何不閃避是件壞事情<br />\n從來未察覺你每個動作<br />\n沒有聲 竟有拍攝的鐵證<br />\n為何苦不讓位亦是罪名 為何總不讓位就是扮型<br />\n從來未察覺你語氣動聽<br />\n在你呼吸聲早已說明<br />\n坐位不可用車票保證"},{"pid":"4ebff9874300e75c9f7595f80b8e3ed0142199d1","tid":45573,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"4b04ddfedf26697b96fa4288dd742bd06357e038","tid":45573,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91401f4a1987a4eecf0425971a2580839c63a859","tid":45573,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cf41f4f6b875ac2d9a1b57ff3bf82dc65331514","tid":45573,"uid":12670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"e292f6801ab70a84bf5cac99e657f36bb1a78e4b","tid":45573,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6cc6d34425c5515aab24d2ddc76676970780d4","tid":45573,"uid":20965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n在你呼吸聲早已說明<br />\n坐位不可用車<span style=\"color: red;\">飛</span>保證</blockquote>"}]}